                            <h4>Permanent Staffing</h4>
                            <ul class="list-unstyled">
                                <li><i class="ri-check-double-line"></i> <b>Job Analysis:-</b> The first step in the process is to analyze the job requirements, responsibilities, and qualifications necessary for a specific position. This helps in understanding the skills and attributes needed in a candidate.</li>
                                <li><i class="ri-check-double-line"></i> <b>Sourcing Candidates:-</b> There are various methods for sourcing candidates, including online job portals, employee referrals, professional networks, social media platforms, and recruitment agencies. These channels are utilized to attract potential candidates who match the desired criteria.</li>
                            </ul>
